high_descs: Turn around, move around the island to the right, keep going until you reach the microwave on the counter to the left.
Take the potato out of the microwave.
Bring the potato to the fridge on the right.
Chill the potato in the fridge.
Take the chilled potato from the fridge and turn around to face the island.
Put the chilled potato on the island.
anns.task_desc: Put a chilled potato on the island.

high_descs: Turn around and walk forward, then turn right and walk around the kitchen island to the microwave in the corner
Open the microwave and pick up the potato from it
Turn left and walk over to the fridge
Put the potato in the fridge then remove it
Turn around and walk up to the kitchen island
Put the potato on the kitchen island
anns.task_desc: Put the chilled potato on the kitchen island

high_descs: Turn around and walk around the left side of kitchen island, veering right into the right corner with the microwave.
Take the egg out of the microwave.
Turn left and walk around the counter to the fridge.
Place the egg in the fridge to the left of the lettuce. Close the door, wait a moment, and take it out again.
Turn around and face the counter.
Place the egg on the counter to the left of the handle of the pan.
anns.task_desc: Place a chilled egg on a counter.
